  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/38409169ddb5434836bb3faa29e1c7d3.avif?t=1747835645\" width=800 height=333 /></span><strong></strong><br><br><br><strong>half-a-cado </strong>is a  puzzle game where you control a numbered cube rolling through grid-based levels filled with mathematical operations. Each move changes your cube's value as you interact with different tiles. Plan your path carefully, solve the mathematical challenges, and reach the goal in as few moves as possible in this uniquely satisfying puzzle experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/b21099fd5b78da4215b4764bdb5b13c9.poster.avif?t=1747835645\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/b21099fd5b78da4215b4764bdb5b13c9.webm?t=1747835645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/b21099fd5b78da4215b4764bdb5b13c9.mp4?t=1747835645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roll & Calculate</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every operation tile changes your value in increasingly complex ways. Work out the most efficient path to reach the target number!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/f6db77d49efb43116f827e0ed3a58d47.poster.avif?t=1747835645\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/f6db77d49efb43116f827e0ed3a58d47.webm?t=1747835645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/f6db77d49efb43116f827e0ed3a58d47.mp4?t=1747835645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five Worlds</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 5 different vegetable themed worlds. Each one introducing a new mathematical operation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/cde0afd78f131adabda92e0b4407feed.poster.avif?t=1747835645\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/cde0afd78f131adabda92e0b4407feed.webm?t=1747835645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/cde0afd78f131adabda92e0b4407feed.mp4?t=1747835645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Increasing Complexity</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about a range of different mathematical operations including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Addition / Subtraction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplication / Division</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Squares</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Factorials</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modulos</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3676060/extras/aedeef71a22576ed6533a86d09ea7d32.avif?t=1747835645\" width=630 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are a two man game studio making one game a month! We've made 5 games so far and this is the first one we are putting on Steam. Stay tuned for more games!</p>",
